sentences: Visan Yonjan (Nepali: भिसान योञ्जन; born 2 October 1981) is a Nepali singer-songwriter.
He began his music career in 2006.
And in 2006, he released his debut album Premiere.
2006Visan's career began as a pop singer when he signed up with Reeyaz Music Records and recorded a debut album in 2006 that brought him further into the limelight.

The Groovers was formed in 2010 by Visan Yonjan after Stoned Amp got disbanded.

The band's second single 'Chaahanna Ma' was released on 24 August 2012 which reached topcharts on the Nepal Mainstream Rock band.
They released their third single 'Jiwan ko paanama' on 5 December 2013; the single marked a change in Visan N' The Groovers's music in a slightly more glam/melo rock influenced direction.
On 8 May 2016, Visan N' The Groovers has released their latest single 'Adrishya' from Inline Creation Records.
